snippet.title: Nintendo Land E3 2012 Trailer
snippet.description: Nintendo Land E3 2012 Trailer: Nintendo Land is the on-board theme park that's packaged with the Wii U. take a look at what to expect in this NintendoLand trailer from the Nintendo presentation from E3 2012. Impressed, or do you think it's like home with a roller coaster? Let us know!
